name: airs-co2-data-may-2003
notes:
Description
---------------

Data from the Atmospheric Infrared Sounder (AIRS) from May 1 2003 to June 1 2003.

Format
---------

The file is in csv format with 8 columns, 

- year: year
- month: month
- day: day
- lat: latitude
- lon: longitude
- solzen: solar zenith angle
- co2avgret: co2 concentration
- co2std: co2 uncertainty (sd)
title: AIRS CO2 data, May 2003
